Class RemoteLookupManagerImpl

All Implemented Interfaces:
RemoteGridNode, LookupManager
public class RemoteLookupManagerImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements LookupManager, RemoteGridNode

This will provide a connection to a specific grid location. It will return all of the search criteria back to the CompositeLookupManager for it to return back to the user.
